data.description: Discover the epitome of luxury living in this stunning home nestled within the coveted Harbor Concourse neighborhood. With a perfect blend of style, functionality, and convenience, this home offers a lifestyle of comfort and sophistication. Boasting five bedrooms and four bathrooms, this home provides ample space for a growing family or those who love to entertain. The first floor features a full bedroom and bathroom, providing a private and convenient space for guests, in-laws, or a home office. This versatile layout caters to a variety of lifestyles. The gourmet kitchen is the perfect place to host holidays! The accordion sliding glass doors also open up to the extended screened in lanai with retractable screens which offer additional space. Ascend to the second floor and discover a spacious loft, perfect for a playroom, home theater, or additional living space. Enjoy the perks of living in the Harbor Concourse neighborhood without the burden of CDD fees and with low HOA fees.
